@startuml sequence-extract-cv
' =====================================================================
' Module 1 — AI RESUME EXTRACTION  (Use Case UC04 + UC23)
' Flow: Upload CV (PDF/TXT) → trích text → DeepSeek trả structured JSON
'       (skills, soft_skills, experience, education, languages, ...)
' Endpoint: POST /api/recommendations/extract-cv
' =====================================================================
!theme plain
skinparam maxMessageSize 160
skinparam ArrowFontSize 11
autonumber

title Module 1 — AI Resume Extraction (UC04 + UC23)\nUpload CV → trích xuất structured JSON bằng DeepSeek

actor "Ứng viên" as User
participant "AIScoreModal\n(Frontend)" as Modal
participant "recommendationService\n(apiClient)" as Api
participant "RecommendationController" as Ctrl
participant "promptBuilder" as Prompt
participant "deepseekClient" as DS
database "DeepSeek API\n(ngoài hệ thống)" as AI <<external>>
participant "aiLogger" as Logger
database "Supabase DB\n(ai_matching_log)" as DB
collections "ai-lab/logs/*.json" as File <<file>>

User -> Modal: Upload file CV (.pdf / .txt / .doc)
Modal -> Modal: pdfjs-dist đọc PDF trong browser\n→ resumeText (cắt tối đa 8000 ký tự)
Modal -> Api: POST /recommendations/extract-cv {resumeText}
Api -> Ctrl: extractCv(req)
Ctrl -> Ctrl: Validate resumeText ≥ 20 ký tự
Ctrl -> Prompt: buildResumeExtractionPrompt(resumeText)
note right of Prompt: Yêu cầu DeepSeek trả JSON đúng schema:\nskills[], soft_skills[], total_experience_years,\neducation_level, languages[], certifications[],\nwork_experience[], summary
Prompt --> Ctrl: messages[] (system + user)
Ctrl -> DS: chatCompletion({task:'resume_extraction', messages})

DS -> AI: POST {BASE_URL}/chat/completions\nheaders: Authorization: Bearer <API_KEY>\nbody: {model, messages, temperature:0,\n      response_format:{type:'json_object'}}
AI --> DS: {choices[0].message.content,\n   usage{prompt_tokens, completion_tokens}}

DS -> Logger: logAiCall({task, model, prompt, response,\n   processingTimeMs, tokensIn/Out, success, metadata})
activate Logger
Logger -> DB: INSERT INTO ai_matching_log\n(prompt_text, response_text, model_name,\n task, tokens_in/out, processing_time_ms)
Logger -> File: writeFile ai_<timestamp>.json
deactivate Logger

DS --> Ctrl: {content, tokensIn, tokensOut}
Ctrl -> Ctrl: JSON.parse(content)\n(báo 502 Bad Gateway nếu sai format)
Ctrl --> Api: 200 OK {extracted, tokensIn, tokensOut}
Api --> Modal: CV có cấu trúc
Modal --> User: Sẵn sàng chấm điểm với CV vừa trích xuất

@enduml
